tool_description: Highly flexible search over thousands of low-carb/keto recipes with rich nutrients information.

api_list.name: Search for Recipes
api_list.description: Search for recipes that match provided criteria.

optional_parameters.name: maxNetCarbs
optional_parameters.description: Maximum net carbs (total carbs subtract fiber and sugar alcohols) of 1 serving in grams.

optional_parameters.name: limit
optional_parameters.description: Max number of results to return.

optional_parameters.name: maxCalories
optional_parameters.description: Maximum calories of 1 serving in KCal.

optional_parameters.name: excludeIngredients
optional_parameters.description: Semicolon separated terms to be excluded in ingredients.

optional_parameters.name: tags
optional_parameters.description: Semicolon separated tags to filter recipes.

optional_parameters.name: name
optional_parameters.description: Search terms to be included in the recipe name.

optional_parameters.name: maxAddedSugar
optional_parameters.description: Maximum added sugar of 1 serving in grams.

optional_parameters.name: maxSugar
optional_parameters.description: Maximum sugar of 1 serving in grams.

optional_parameters.name: includeIngredients
optional_parameters.description: Semicolon separated terms to be included in ingredients.

api_list.name: Get recipe by ID
api_list.description: Get details of the specified recipe by its ID.

required_parameters.name: recipeId
required_parameters.description: Recipe ID to fetch the specific recipe details.
